file.name: me_admin_spec.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: kearch meta search engine admin API
  description: kearch meta search engine admin API
  version: 0.1.0
servers:
  - url: '{scheme}://{me_host}:{port}/me/admin'
    variables:
      scheme:
        enum:
          - http
          - https
        default: http
      me_host:
        default: localhost
      port:
        default: '32600'
paths:
  /login:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: username
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
        - in: query
          name: password
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
  /logout:
    get:
      summary:
  /update_password:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                required: true
                password:
                  type: string
                password_again:
                  type: string
  /learn_params_for_evaluator:
    get:
      summary:
  /approve_a_connection_request:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                required: true
                sp_host:
                  type: string
  /delete_a_connection_request:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                required: true
                sp_host:
                  type: string
  /send_a_connection_request:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                required: true
                sp_host:
                  type: string
